        <h2>Understanding Apostille and Attestation for UAE</h2>

        <p>The <strong>UAE is not a member of the Hague Apostille Convention</strong>. This is a crucial fact that affects how all foreign documents are processed for use in the Emirates.</p>

        <div class="comparison-box">
