          <p><strong>An apostille from a Hague-member country simplifies the first step of authentication</strong> ‚Äî it replaces notarisation and home country foreign ministry attestation in one step. However, it does NOT eliminate the need for UAE Embassy attestation and MOFA attestation.</p>
          <p><strong>Always confirm requirements with your specific employer's PRO (Public Relations Officer) or the government entity you're dealing with BEFORE starting the attestation process.</strong></p>
